  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComplexExpansionMethod<Interaction,​BinaryInteraction>
    public class MatrixExpansion
extends AbstractMatrixExpansion<Interaction,​BinaryInteraction>
    The matrix Expansion method. Complex n-ary data has been expanded to binary using the spoke model. This assumes that all molecules in the complex interact with each other.
    Since:
    04/06/13
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
